THE DIFFERENCE

At Dr. Pink Orthodontics, the difference is clear—personalized, board-certified care from start to finish, with no handoffs, no long waits, and no compromises.

Tap to 📱 Call →
(805) 643-7516

Unlike large chain practices, Dr. Pink Orthodontics ensures every patient is seen exclusively by Dr. Cassandra Pinkerous— a board-certified specialist—using advanced technology, flexible scheduling, and custom treatment plans designed for comfort, efficiency, and long-lasting, confident smiles you’ll love.

Meet Dr. Pink

Why Choose Dr. Pink Orthodontics

Because your smile deserves more than average—get expert care from a board-certified orthodontist who puts precision, comfort, and personalization at the heart of every treatment.

Board-Certified Expertise You Can Trust

Dr. Cassandra Pinkerous is a board-certified orthodontist—an elite designation earned by only a select few. This means you get top-tier care backed by rigorous training, clinical excellence, and a commitment to ongoing education.

Why It Matters

We Accept Insurance—Even Out-of-Network

Worried about coverage? We accept most PPO insurance plans and help you maximize your benefits, even if we're out-of-network. Affordable care starts with smart, flexible options.

Check Insurance

Care That’s Fully Personalized—Always by Dr. Pink

At our practice, you’re not passed around. Every visit, every plan, every adjustment is made by Dr. Pinkerous herself. No handoffs. Just consistent, customized care from start to finish.
